該遠遠多過非香港人<br />\n自損十個可能先損到敵人一個</blockquote><br />\n點只 廿年百五隻蝗 未計落黎讀書 再住夠七年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b0d875f29ed462ce28b34cb00aa1893bf14914","tid":446504,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T02:13:22.000Z","msg":"紅十字會繼續覺得自己冇問題，問你死未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3781809bef863cbe71adb48f812412b4f2ee88","tid":446504,"uid":78165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T05:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe100d765921b9f14d58eff8b1871657a172e6e","tid":446504,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:50:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紅十字會繼續覺得自己冇問題，問你死未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2764c3bfff34b7084490195d29f8a229c6ce30b8","tid":446504,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:54:01.000Z","msg":"真香港人應該建立自己既血庫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e50f6e88ddfba02a81d37544616b1bedfc0eba","tid":446504,"uid":10692,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:56:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ee0f119c7e6609bed79e11e6366693caf7374d6","tid":446504,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:57:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真香港人應該建立自己既血庫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagree"},{"pid":"fc75ba96ea16945e11387c9587d59053827fcf71","tid":446504,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:58:54.000Z","msg"